latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So after 4 years i decided to pick up a chreography and dance my heart out. Boy it was tough! Was out of practise for such a long time,easily tired,did not have the same finesse as I used to have but somehow managed to practise this in 4 hours!! Tried @sonali.bhadauria choreography but had to improvise coz she was too good and difficult to catch up🙈 Enjoy!
Song : Ghungroo
